- **Contact form** → `generate_lead` on successful submission
- **Exit intent popup** → `calendly_click`
- **Contact page** Calendly link → `calendly_click`
- **Contact page** WhatsApp link → `whatsapp_click`
- Created `src/types/gtag.d.ts` for TypeScript support

### 5. Sitemap Updated ✅
- Date updated to `2026-03-20`
- All 4 new location pages added with `priority: 0.8`

### 6. Favicon ✅
- Created `public/favicon.ico` (amber-colored placeholder)
- Added `icons` metadata to `layout.tsx` (favicon.ico, 16x16, 32x32, apple-touch-icon)

### 7. Meta Tags & Keyword Targeting ✅
- Homepage title changed to: `"Osama Tahir | Web Developer & Digital Marketing Specialist Dubai, UAE"`
- OG + Twitter titles updated to match
- Added keywords: "Freelance web developer Dubai", "Website design Dubai", "Web developer Sharjah", "SEO services Abu Dhabi"
- Hero subtitle updated with "freelance web developer" keyword naturally

### 8. Image Alt Text ✅
- Profile photo alt text improved to include keywords: "Freelance Web Developer and Digital Marketing Specialist in Dubai, UAE"

### 9. llms.txt Updated ✅
- Added all 4 location pages with descriptions
- Added social links: Instagram, Twitter/X, Facebook, GitHub
- Updated location to list all 7 UAE emirates

### 10. Robots.txt ✅ (already correct)
- Already allows GPTBot, ClaudeBot, PerplexityBot, Googlebot, Bingbot, Google-Extended
